Usage
=====
python needleprojection.py

Create Example Image
====================
c3d -create 256x256x160 1x1x1mm -o newimage.vtk

Visualize Needle
================
/opt/apps/Paraview/ParaView-4.0.1-Linux-64bit/bin/paraview --data=needle.vtk
/opt/apps/Paraview/ParaView-3.14.1-Linux-64bit/bin/paraview --data=needle.vtk
